WEBVTT

00:00:00.720 --> 00:00:03.630
Well, good evening everybody. Merry

00:00:03.640 --> 00:00:06.870
Christmas from our house to yours. We

00:00:06.880 --> 00:00:09.670
pray you had a wonderful Christmas with

00:00:09.680 --> 00:00:12.470
your family and friends, or whatever

00:00:12.470 --> 00:00:12.480
y'all

00:00:12.480 --> 00:00:14.470
did. If you had something good to

00:00:14.480 --> 00:00:16.950
eat, you celebrate Jesus.

00:00:16.960 --> 00:00:18.870
Jesus is the reason for the

00:00:18.880 --> 00:00:20.990
season. Wasn't it wonderful to celebrate

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:22.470
our King today?

00:00:22.480 --> 00:00:25.550
We had our birthday cake, and Paisley

00:00:25.560 --> 00:00:27.550
said, "Daddy, we got to go get

00:00:27.560 --> 00:00:30.350
Jesus a birthday cake."So we went to

00:00:30.360 --> 00:00:32.230
the ice cream store. They had

00:00:32.240 --> 00:00:33.590
ice cream cakes,

00:00:33.590 --> 00:00:33.600
and

00:00:33.600 --> 00:00:34.830
Paisley said, "Do you think he'd want ice

00:00:34.840 --> 00:00:36.750
cream cake today?"I said, "Well, I

00:00:36.760 --> 00:00:38.550
think that's better than the one we got

00:00:38.560 --> 00:00:41.255
last year."So we went and got one

00:00:41.265 --> 00:00:43.190
of those. Paisley was so

00:00:43.200 --> 00:00:44.910
excited. The

00:00:44.920 --> 00:00:46.350
lady asked, "Who do you want to put

00:00:46.360 --> 00:00:48.350
on the birthday cake?"and we said,

00:00:48.360 --> 00:00:50.630
"Jesus, it's his birthday."She just

00:00:50.640 --> 00:00:52.110
looked at us like we're nuts. She said,

00:00:52.120 --> 00:00:53.710
"I won't put it on there; I'll have the

00:00:53.720 --> 00:00:55.590
