00:00:55.600 --> 00:00:57.670
Christian. But that was all right because we

00:00:57.680 --> 00:01:00.350
got to share the light of God

00:01:00.360 --> 00:01:02.550
to that lady in the cake store. It

00:01:02.550 --> 00:01:02.560
was

00:01:02.560 --> 00:01:05.270
pretty neat.

00:01:05.280 --> 00:01:07.310
People don't get it, but we love to

00:01:07.320 --> 00:01:09.950
celebrate Jesus. I

00:01:09.960 --> 00:01:11.510
was out and I was

00:01:11.520 --> 00:01:13.110
praying this morning

00:01:13.120 --> 00:01:15.230
and I said, "Lord, do you want me to

00:01:15.240 --> 00:01:17.350
do a live stream today

00:01:17.360 --> 00:01:19.590
