00:01:22.880 --> 00:01:24.790
traditional.

00:01:24.800 --> 00:01:27.270
I want you to tell them something

00:01:27.280 --> 00:01:29.630
different. Everybody has focused

00:01:29.640 --> 00:01:31.390
on my first coming

00:01:31.400 --> 00:01:32.510
today,

00:01:32.520 --> 00:01:35.510
that I came and

00:01:35.520 --> 00:01:37.510
sacrificed my life for you. But

00:01:37.520 --> 00:01:39.990
Brandon, I'm coming again

00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:42.070
and I want you to tell them what you saw

00:01:42.080 --> 00:01:43.630
in the tribulation.

00:01:43.640 --> 00:01:45.350
I want you to go over and

00:01:45.360 --> 00:01:46.630
shake them

00:01:46.640 --> 00:01:48.310
