00:01:48.320 --> 00:01:50.030
Many people

00:01:50.040 --> 00:01:53.950
are asleep;

00:01:53.960 --> 00:01:56.310
many people don't realize the

00:01:56.320 --> 00:01:59.030
seriousness of the hour,

00:01:59.030 --> 00:01:59.040
Brandon."I

00:01:59.040 --> 00:02:00.910
said, "Lord, that's not a traditional

00:02:00.920 --> 00:02:03.070
Christmas message, but I'll do what

00:02:03.080 --> 00:02:04.670
